ntor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"7af1913\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-784f689\" data-id=\"784f689\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e98084b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e98084b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Company Information<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9f271fd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9f271fd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Juvas is one of the leading Indian technological companies and an end-to-end solution provider in the Power Distribution Equipment industry. Based in Kolkata, Juvas has been manufacturing a wide range of electrical products in the Eastern, Northern and Western parts of India for the last 5 decades.<\/p><p>Juvas has a strong Pan-India presence. Already spread across 5 countries, Juvas aims at creating a strong global presence. Our Pan-India operations is managed through various offices &amp; Manufacturing units in Kolkata, Noida and Delhi. We have a network of around 20,000+ dealers, distributors and retailers.<\/p><p>One of the leading manufacturers of Consumer and Industrial Electrical Products such as LED Lights, Switches &amp; Accessories, Wires &amp; Cables, Switchgears, Fans, Meters, Conduits &amp; Fittings, Poles, etc., Juvas Products are approved by all major government and semi-government departments, along with being certified by the Bureau of Indian Standards, providing certification of quality, safety and reliability. Our products are self \u2013 designed and tested after a great deal of R&amp;D work. Our strength lies in our products being extremely affordable with premium quality and latest designs.<\/p><p>Other brands owned by the Parent Company UTC (Universal Trade Centre) apart from Juvas are Juvas Pro, Universal, Elektron, Sega and Jaivic.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-48cac69 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"48cac69\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;gradient&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-9218758\" data-id=\"9218758\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-058c19b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section